# IoT Device Telemetry API

MQTT-based API for IoT device telemetry and control

HOST: mqtt://iot.example.com:1883

## /devices/{deviceId}/commands [/devices/{deviceId}/commands]

Commands sent to devices

### Device receives commands [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

## /devices/{deviceId}/status [/devices/{deviceId}/status]

Device status and health information

### Device publishes status updates [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

## /devices/{deviceId}/telemetry [/devices/{deviceId}/telemetry]

Device telemetry data stream

### Device publishes telemetry data [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

